11#include "modules/video_coding/unique_timestamp_counter.h"
12
13#include <cstdint>
14#include <memory>
15#include <set>
16
17namespace webrtc {
18namespace {
19
20constexpr int kMaxHistory = 1000;
21
22} // namespace
23
24UniqueTimestampCounter::UniqueTimestampCounter()
25 : latest_(std::make_unique<uint32_t[]>(kMaxHistory)) {}
26
27void UniqueTimestampCounter::Add(uint32_t value) {
28 if (value == last_ || !search_index_.insert(value).second) {
29 // Already known.
30 return;
31 }
32 int index = unique_seen_ % kMaxHistory;
33 if (unique_seen_ >= kMaxHistory) {
34 search_index_.erase(latest_[index]);
35 }
36 latest_[index] = value;
37 last_ = value;
38 ++unique_seen_;
39}
40
41} // namespace webrtc
